snippet.title: Sweet Dreams Preview -  "The Great Tatalov" | Honkai: Star Rail
snippet.description:
"Greetings, outworlder. My name is Shatana, and I have a deal to offer you..."
"How are you able to understand what I'm saying, you ask? Don't you have a 'Synesthesia Beacon'?"
* Shatana's voice will be translated by a special Synesthesia Beacon in the video.
* For more storyline previews, please stay tuned for the Version 2.0 Special Program on 01/26

English Voice:
Shatana — Elizabeth  Maxwell
Himeko — Cia Court
Firefly — Analesa  Fisher
Sampo — Roger Rose
